OL,3,CDartford Crossing charge will rise in
OL,4,CSeptember to 'manage traffic'
OL,6,FThe charge motorists pay to use the
OL,7,FDartford Crossing will increase in
OL,8,FSeptember, a minister has said.
OL,10,FUsed by an average of more than
OL,11,F150,000 vehicles a day, the crossing
OL,12,Fis made up of a bridge and two tunnels
OL,13,Fand connects Thurrock in Essex with
OL,14,FDartford in Kent.
