OL,3,CDartford Crossing charge will rise in
OL,4,CSeptember to 'manage traffic'
OL,6,FLilian Greenwood, Parliamentary under-
OL,7,FSecretary at the Department for
OL,8,FTransport, said in a statement on
OL,9,FTuesday that the existing one-off
OL,10,Fpayment for cars, motorhomes and small
OL,11,Fminibuses of #2.50 will be increased
OL,12,Fto #3.50 from September 1 to "manage
OL,13,Ftraffic".
OL,15,FCharges were first introduced in 2003
OL,16,Fand prices have not increased since
OL,17,F2014, the minister said.
