OL,3,CDartford Crossing charge will rise in
OL,4,CSeptember to 'manage traffic'
OL,6,FWith up to 180,000 vehicles using the
OL,7,Fcrossing on the busiest days, Ms
OL,8,FGreenwood described the traffic levels
OL,9,Fas "well in excess of the crossing's
OL,10,Fdesign capacity, causing delays for
OL,11,Fdrivers using the crossing, congestion
OL,12,Fand journey disruption to drivers on
OL,13,Fthe M25 and a range of knock-on
OL,14,Fimpacts for local communities".
OL,16,FMotorcycles, moped and quad bikes will
OL,17,Fstill be able to use the route free of
OL,18,Fcharge.
