OL,3,CDartford Crossing charge will rise in
OL,4,CSeptember to 'manage traffic'
OL,6,FThe one-off payment for buses, coaches
OL,7,Fand vans with two axles will rise from
OL,8,F#3 to #4.20, while the one-off price
OL,9,Ffor vehicles with more than two axles
OL,10,Fwill increase from #6 to #8.40.
OL,12,FLocal residents who currently pay #20
OL,13,Fa year to use the Dartford Crossing as
OL,14,Fmany times as they want will have to
OL,15,Fpay #25 from September 1.
OL,17,FJourneys made between the hours of
OL,18,F10pm and 6am will continue to be free.
